posting_body: ['This property is listed by Wendy Legeros, licensed agent with Complete Management Services.', 'ST.', 'BONIFACIUS RENTAL PROPERTY 4385, 2BR $1,395/month', 'IDPROP-\xad4385', 'Listing type:', 'For Rent', 'Bedrooms 2+loft', 'Bathrooms 1.5', 'Pets No pets', 'Living Area 1100 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Deposit $1395', 'Property type: Townhome', 'Parking 1 car attached garage', 'Location St. Bonifacius, MN', 'Lease Term 12 month minimum', 'Available September 1, 2022', 'PROPERTY DESCRIPTION', '8969 Partridge Road, St. Bonifacius, MN 55375', 'St. Bonifacius Rental Property 4385, 2BR', 'Lovely two level townhome located in charming small town community with easy access to the Dakota Trail for all of you biking enthusiasts.', 'Many great features including a spacious open kitchen, Good size bedrooms(master has walk in closet) and laundry on the same floor as the bedrooms for added convenience.', 'There is a City park right across the street for those with children, grandchildren etc.', 'Owner looking for quiet, responsible renters.', 'No smoking.', 'Application fee is $60 per adult, $65 for out of state applicants.', 'ADDITIONAL FEATURES', '2 Levels Carpet Dishwasher Eat In Kitchen In Unit Laundry Large Bedrooms Lawn Care and Snow Removal Included Loft Area Neutral Decor Park Across Street', 'Patio Refrigerator Stove Trash And Water Included Walk-In Closet']
